{
  "stem": "4247.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was mainly, mainly keeping you alive, keeping yourself clean, filling up your stomach, talking about, about [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the world things.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were very interested what was happening in the world, right?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Political and military dispatches were always tremendously-- interest to us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And And how did they come to you?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It must have been very, very isolated.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, look, we always had this-- I mean, the, the source of true information was the BBC, the, the British Broadcasting Corporation, who was the only source at the time who could provide us the occasional news.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they were-- we did not listen to it ourselves because we, we had no radio and we had no opportunity of even-- we didn't dare to do that.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "However, we did have rumors circulating.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they are usually centered around what other people who had access to the would have heard the night before.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, Fried Gezer, for example, our, our leader there, right, had such access, right?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he very discreetly would have told us, right-- but very discreetly, it wasn't an open discussion-- that you know, did you hear that Voronezh fell last night, you know?",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that was tremendous.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because we are acutely interested in that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we were very knowledgeable, as far as the geography is concerned, right?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We knew exactly where Voronezh is.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we could relate it to the-- we could draw military conclusions from it, right?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Hmm.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "All right, so from the timber work that you did and-- I've forgotten the name already in the--",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Arlo.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were there-- [SIGHS] we were there, I would say-- [SIGHS] I would say, we would have been there until late July, early August--",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--I would say.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Meanwhile, as I said earlier, they deported my parents, and--",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
